===Adjective===
'''hard''' (''[[comparative]]'' '''harder''', ''[[superlative]]'' '''hardest''')

#Resistant to pressure.
#Requiring a lot of [[effort]] to do or understand
#:''a hard problem''
#Demanding a lot of effort to endure.
#:''a hard life''
#Of a person, [[severe]], [[unfriendly]].
#[[Unquestionable]].
#:''hard evidence''
#Of drink, [[strong]].
#Of water, high in [[dissolve]]d [[calcium]] [[compound]]s.

